{"tid":2513683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想做殯儀行業，有無咩方法可以入行","createTime":"2021-05-02T16:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T23:22:03.000Z","uid":243511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3efa11e5e8f4fd9bd8f540a262f279ee01e2c6a3","tid":2513683,"uid":243511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"其實早幾年屋企有兩位長輩相繼離世已經對呢行有興趣<br />\n覺得做殯儀服務好神聖<br />\n早排睇到一條YouTube片介紹殯儀行業<br />\n又勾返起興趣<br />\n呢幾日同屋企人講起都無反對，但奈何無渠道入行<br />\n如果有巴打絲打可以介紹我入行我唔介意人工，由零學起"},{"pid":"024362865e8e46e62136ce92d00e079860a803df","tid":2513683,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"殯儀依行好封閉<br />\n入行好講關係"},{"pid":"e5343ea381d3fa87ba0cfffae92336340edca41e","tid":2513683,"uid":98929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"d2fe3c7af34858a7f4448be0635ebc6063bcbe98","tid":2513683,"uid":243511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"024362865e8e46e62136ce92d00e079860a803df","tid":2513683,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"殯儀依行好封閉<br />\n入行好講關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"睇到有啲採訪新聞都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都知好難入行 我都係試問下"},{"pid":"8487573a936d93f0c1f297ed492900eb4733c1dd","tid":2513683,"uid":309357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"直接入去講我想做，請唔請，可以由低做起？咁都怕，懦夫"},{"pid":"37d073ef181e0dbf81ca722475c6d3aea093093b","tid":2513683,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T20:37:10.000Z","msg":"初入行<br />\n冇人工架"},{"pid":"1e85b354d1d17e9dd64801ac2b6ea128f13f02da","tid":2513683,"uid":13835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:06:15.000Z","msg":"識唔識扮爆旋陀螺轉"},{"pid":"1b3928e2257e60f330a8a9c2e5bc48355692bb53","tid":2513683,"uid":228213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quo